  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">A bathroom for Santi</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Santi&apos;s family does not have a bathroom. The nights and early mornings in the Popocatepetl Volcano area are very cold. Santi cannot have a warm bath before going to school and has to use an outhouse when going to the toilet. Help us build this families a bathroom (with sink, shower and toilet), a rainwater collection system, a solar water heater and a biodigestor for turning waste into compost.</narrative>
  </description>
